# LOTW replay fixture v1
# Format:
#   frame <count> [buttons...]
# Buttons use these names: up down left right A B start select.
#
# This fixture starts the game, selects Pochi from the family selection screen,
# then walks left inside the house. It stores only controller timing, not ROM
# data or captured frames.
frame 300
frame 12 start
frame 180
frame 120 right
frame 42 up
frame 12 A
frame 120 left
frame 120
